Results.ReviewText: Buy this regularly for my husband as he goes fishing and finds carrying a tin much easier than having a glass jar in his bag. It is a lovely flavour coffee very rich but smooth at the same time.
Results.Title: Smooth flavour

Results.ReviewText: Gorgeous smooth tasting coffee as if you've just collected it from your local coffee shop. No queues, no grinding beans, no expensive machinery required, no pods to dispose of - Instant heaven!
Results.Title: Barista style & taste without the hassle

Results.ReviewText: I tried this coffee because it was on offer and OMG it was amazing, it has a nice sweet taste and creamy, (try frothing your milk with a spoonful of coffee then add your hot water) wonderful.
Results.Title: Check this out!!

Results.ReviewText: This is my morning treat in work - a nice cup of Azera coffee and a few moments peace! It has a genuinely filter coffee taste and feel - without needing to bring a coffee machine to work!
Results.Title: Full flavour

Results.ReviewText: I don't like ordinary coffee, only percolated or from a cafetiere.  I had a sample of Azera and a money off voucher so tried it.  Its the closest taste to either of those and I love it.
Results.Title: Love the taste

Results.ReviewText: Have tried all the varieties and each one is amazing. Easy to make and tastes more expensive than it actually is! Highly recommended- - have already got friends to change to this brand
Results.Title: Just like drinking out!

Results.ReviewText: I tried this for the first time last week I'm not a coffe drinker. But my friend had no tea so she made me a Americano omg if I had this year's ago is be a coffe drinker. I LOVE  IT.
Results.Title: smooth and creamy

Results.ReviewText: I am completely addicted to Azera Americano - will only drink this if I have a choice, only coffee I will buy and really wish there was a decaf version to make my life complete.
Results.Title: Only coffee I will buy

Results.ReviewText:
I start drinking Americano abot 6 months ago. it's so far the best instant I have ever tried.
Smoth taste and Aroma close to real coffee so excellent instant coffee.
Results.Title: Excellent instant coffee

Results.ReviewText: This little tin of goodness is just the thing for a work time coffee break. Azera has a great taste that hits the spot, even if you only have 5 minutes to make it.
Results.Title: Perfect for the work time coffee break

Results.ReviewText: I have changed my coffee habbits to Azera Americano and have not looked back. The only difference from drinking an intant rather than a fresh coffee is the PRICE!
Results.Title: Feels like a costa every day

Results.ReviewText: Love this coffee, as good as coffee shop in my opinion, I have saved loads making my own coffee to go in the morning, the can keeps it fresh to the last cup too.
Results.Title: Delicious and easy

Results.ReviewText: Started drinking coffee 4 - 6 weeks ago love all the different types including cappocino and latte there should be more flavours full time not just seasonal
Results.Title: Choices

Results.ReviewText: When  you  cannot  get  to  your favourite  coffee shop  this  does the trick and keeps you  topped up  from  home-as good as any  barista would  serve you!
Results.Title: Aauthentic Americano!

Results.ReviewText: I bought for first time last year this kind of coffee and I didn't look back i absolutely love it, and my work colleges are hooked to Azera Americano
Results.Title: LOve This Coffe

Results.ReviewText: I have been buying this, and only this since trying it by chance on special offer about a year ago - full of flavour smooth and a real coffee taste.
Results.Title: Real Coffee!

Results.ReviewText: I was given some samples of this a while ago and have continued to buy Azera Americano ever since, I just love the flavour, the taste is  wonderful
Results.Title: Fantastic flavour

Results.ReviewText: A friend introduced me to this coffee, i love the flavour and i also like the espresso and i have been known to mix the two for a stronger flavour
Results.Title: great taste

Results.ReviewText: Azera is a smooth coffee with no bitter aftertaste. You need very little for an intense coffee hit so it is great VFM too. Just love this product
Results.Title: Smooth but flavoursome

Results.ReviewText: I actually bought this for my son in law when he was visiting and thought I would try it too, but it was too strong for me. He liked it, though.
Results.Title: Not for me!

Results.ReviewText: I would say Azera americano is the nearest instant coffee to taste like a coffee drink in a coffee shop. It is smooth, but still full of flavour
Results.Title: cafe excellence

Results.ReviewText: I first tried this coffee as it was on special offer, started using at both work and home and now it is the preferred coffee within the office.
Results.Title: Great flavoured coffee

Results.ReviewText: I don't think anyone could possibly dislike this coffee! It's got that freshly ground taste, is lovely and smooth and has no bitterness at all.
Results.Title: A perfect blend for everyone!

Results.ReviewText: Tried this for the first time recently, the closest thing to filtered coffee I have tasted. I would recommend it to everyone. Great taste!
Results.Title: Fabulous Rich Taste

Results.ReviewText: Love this product.  I look out for it when it is on offer and stock up for myself as well as my daughter.  Really flavourful and smooth.
Results.Title: Full bodied and flavourful

Results.ReviewText: I bought this a couple of months ago as I fancied a change from my usual coffee - now I won't switch back. This is my new usual coffee!
Results.Title: My new favourite coffee

Results.ReviewText: This is the only Coffee I will buy and drink! I even carry a tin around in my handbag! Beautiful and smooth and the creama is a bonus!
Results.Title: THE best

Results.ReviewText: I ran out of my Dolce Gusto pods and brought some of this until I could get more it was so good I always make sure I have some in now
Results.Title: Azure Americano

Results.ReviewText: Every morning I drink this smooth coffee to wake me up and put me on the right track for the day. Keeps me tuned into my bright side
Results.Title: Wake me up

Results.ReviewText: I always buy this as no other coffee matches the taste.... I love the coffee creme and the smell is amazing.. Best coffee ever!
Results.Title: Love it! The taste and the smell
